br />\n最近大陸出嘅動畫反攻日本添<br />\n日本11月會上羅小黑戰記電影"},{"pid":"24a42dc94f82a6a922fae73bef7b19ce99bd44bf","tid":2255411,"uid":2607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T21:35:35.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意睇彩色漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a263ed7c4ee6b0fb66e72d5201ba90de530313fa","tid":2255411,"uid":134012,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T21:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWXZuWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWXZuWQ.jpg&h=5ac7f19d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支漫只服鎮魂街"},{"pid":"0bf4263aec7fd976f920d51bed015232447d7bf4","tid":2255411,"uid":217555,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T21:57:40.000Z","msg":"中肯講句 <br />\n國漫根本唔掂 有頭威無尾陣<br />\n以樓主個套原目為例<br />\n一開始的確做到懸疑 未知個種恐懼 令人期待後續劇情<br />\n到後期劇情明朗化 <br />\n伏筆用一 二話草草解釋完就算 <br />\n四五十話走去好遠既地方拿資源<br />\n劇情拖到仆街<br />\n而家係講緊一星期更新一話<br />\n睇成年都係同一個地點 真係屌出黎"},{"pid":"4b2d2fbd12e0465f5c7352b9370a2c97776cddf9","tid":2255411,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"801ac2dc819fdd6b12b15da91bee351971705e3a","tid":2255411,"uid":161190,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T13:55:44.000Z","msg":"我獨自升級 好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T22:01:12.000Z","msg":"我都睇緊 個開頭好掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日輕小說改完全唔係佢果皮"},{"pid":"ba6d7ddbd81bc4eb3b5ab4a0351c64a383ddde23","tid":2255411,"uid":243767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T22:04:07.000Z","msg":"神之塔呢？"},{"pid":"b36cfd39f7e32ff7015ae2fbd92d4637847edc46","tid":2255411,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T22:39:16.000Z","msg":"圖書館的大魔法師<br />\n我有睇，算幾好睇但神作算不上<br />\n<br />\n日本依家行輕小說漫畫動畫化多<br />\n除非你唔計依樣啦"},{"pid":"d8bf577107