"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你睇下最近果套整客液<br />\n我一路睇一路屌<br />\n係條女話想睇先去"},{"pid":"478f263aea623dd8ec25d7fe78eb5cc37c909653","tid":2255411,"uid":60047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a263ed7c4ee6b0fb66e72d5201ba90de530313fa","tid":2255411,"uid":134012,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T21:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWXZuWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWXZuWQ.jpg&h=5ac7f19d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支漫只服鎮魂街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:34:36.000Z","msg":"鎮魂街後期有d悶<br />\n鏢人 真係刺激 好似睇緊火鳳咁"},{"pid":"09996e00060fae711749bc1515239cbf8744cc86","tid":2255411,"uid":250773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f3dd742e8b2c3bcea0eb5020c3ca958a257b235","tid":2255411,"uid":237555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你睇下最近果套整客液<br />\n我一路睇一路屌<br />\n係條女話想睇先去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T20:37:27.000Z","msg":"睇一套動畫戲黎概括個漫畫界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1edcba0bd039942fb8f5d308da2315a15b98670f","tid":2255411,"uid":15496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T17:32:12.000Z","msg":"睇完獨自升級 好正 <br />\n有d似overlord由零開始版<br />\n仲有冇多d韓漫（彩漫）介紹"},{"pid":"fc65dbe2c8683c2f1f2cd87baf1405a4c96b2f0d","tid":2255411,"uid":60527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1edcba0bd039942fb8f5d308